        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Was thinking about these two in comparison. From what i understand, it's basically 15k dmg vs 3-4kish? Plus, 1500 of ours is a 6 tick dot.. How is this fair? You can say oh, wizzy's are for dmg... etc etc, but it comes down to, both of us are trying to do the max ammount of dmg, they win.</P><P>Then there's the fact that "ours is a heal", but technically, ours isn't really a heal because it takes away so much life in the beginning anyways. </P><P>Only advantage of ours that i've thought of is ours doesn't cost mana, so we can keep fighting. I haven't looked at difference in re-use time. I'm not trying to complain, i love necros, but you guys can all tell me to go be a wizzy anyways, hehe.</P><P>What do you guys think</P><P><BR>Darkness will prevail.<BR>55 Defiler.</font></td>

