        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         You're missing the whole damage over time factor, and the huge difference in damage. </P><P>Lifeburn is a max 5k, I've never met a necro who's broken the 5k barrier fully buffed. If we critted it, 10k.</P><P>Wizards, 7500, critted, 15k. Your damage is a hell of a lot more than ours, us critting still wouldn't come close.</P><P>Lets review over time factor. It is not the goal of verant to make any one class deal more damage than another, but due to the difference in mob hp totals, resistances, ac, etc, different classes win out on the damage in different situations. Best case scenerio for Warlocks is a long 500k hp fight on a mob that doesn't resist any spells.</P><P>In this fight, damage should be relatively equal. Staggared a bit over on the melee side as monks/rogues dish out the most. On the caster side, damage is going to go in order of flexibility. Shamman and Necro's with their extremely effecient DoT's should be on the high end, not wizards.</P><P>We'll move onto a different scenerio. 32k Talendor. 5 wizards instantly kill this mob in their first cast of manaburn. None of the Warlocks present have time to land a spell. Here the Wizards obviously take the high end, on the low hp mobs, the quick fights. Those always belong to the Wizard.</P><P>We want more damage, but we never asked to out do a wizard and have all that damage done instantly. When I say Crit DoT's, you could make my Affliction Fury simply increase the durration of my DoT by twice as much. Wizards have Fury and Damage Focus, we only have Affliction extention focus. Where's our Fury? Oh, and could druids and shamman please get it too.</P><P>Stacking DoT's? Capacity is 15 buff/debuff slots on any PC/NPC. If we start stacking DoT's, no spells would ever take hold. Won't happen, don't want it to happen, forget about it. DoT Extention is the answer, Lifeburn crit is the answer.</P><P>Warlock<BR>Shadow Council<BR>Terris-Thule<BR><a href="http://www.shadowcouncil.com" target="_blank">http://www.shadowcouncil.com</a><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6164" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6164</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
